sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant SPA as Stitch Web App (SPA)
  participant API as Stitch API
  participant DB as Metadata DB (tenantId scoped)
  participant S3 as S3 (Tech Packs Bucket)
  participant OS as OpenSearch (Index)
  participant Q as SQS (Ingestion Queue)
  participant L1 as Lambda (Ingestion Orchestrator)
  participant L2 as Lambda (Extract + Chunk)
  participant BR as Bedrock (LLM / Embeddings)

  Note over U,SPA: User opens Upload Files page
  U->>SPA: Navigate to Upload Files
  SPA->>API: GET /files (tenantId, userId)
  API->>DB: Query files by tenantId + userId
  DB-->>API: File list + metadata + status
  API-->>SPA: 200 OK
  SPA-->>U: Render empty state or file list

  Note over U,SPA: User uploads PDF/Excel
  U->>SPA: Select files + Upload
  SPA->>API: POST /uploads (init)
  API->>DB: Create file records (status=Uploading)
  API-->>SPA: Pre-signed S3 URLs + fileIds
  SPA->>S3: PUT file bytes (pre-signed)
  S3-->>SPA: 200 OK
  SPA->>API: POST /uploads/complete (fileIds)
  API->>DB: Update status=Queued, uploadedAt, lastModifiedAt
  API->>Q: Enqueue ingestion job (tenantId, fileId, s3Key)
  API-->>SPA: 202 Accepted

  Note over Q,L1: Async pipeline
  Q-->>L1: SQS message
  L1->>DB: Update status=Indexing
  L1->>L2: Invoke extract job (fileId)

  Note over L2: Extract text, tables, and image-derived text\nRedact user-identifying info before LLM calls
  L2->>S3: GET object
  L2->>L2: Parse PDF/Excel + OCR tables/images
  L2->>L2: Redact PII (sanitized content only)
  L2->>BR: Generate embeddings / structured fields
  BR-->>L2: Embeddings / output
  L2->>OS: Index chunks + metadata (tenantId partition)
  OS-->>L2: 200 OK
  L2->>DB: Update status=Ready, indexedAt

  alt Ingestion failure
    L2->>DB: Update status=Failed, errorCode
  end

  Note over U,SPA: User deletes a file
  U->>SPA: Delete file
  SPA->>API: DELETE /files/{fileId}
  API->>DB: Mark deletedAt (soft delete)
  API->>S3: Delete object
  API->>OS: Delete indexed docs by (tenantId, fileId)
  API-->>SPA: 204 No Content
  SPA-->>U: Remove row from list

